  <brief_title>Daytime Impact Sleep Study</brief_title>
  <acronym>DAISS</acronym>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomised, Parallel-group Trial Investigating Sleep Behaviour and Daytime Performance in Nocturia Patients Treated With Desmopressin Orally Disintegrating Tablets as Compared to Placebo</official_title>
  <sponsors>
